data.description: Elegant Top Floor Condo with Towering Views of Grays Harbor Bay, Lake Minard, Olympic Mountains, and twinkling lights of the City of Westport. Take the convenient elevator to fine dining, local mercantile, or the Beach. Inside you are greeted with a spa-like atmosphere, vaulted ceilings featuring a braided palm ceiling fan, gorgeous kitchen with stainless steel appliances and lots of counter space, storage and eating space. Cozy Propane Fireplace, Private Deck. Grand Primary Bedroom boasts an En-suite with double-sink and walk-in closet. There is another Bedroom off the Entry and second Bathroom with full tub, stackable W/D. Water, sewer, garbage and propane included in the HOA Dues of $279.76/mo.
